<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٦٠⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>إِلَى بَيَاضِ الْجِلْدِ وَيَأْخُذُ هَذَيْنِ يَعْنِي بَيْنَ الشَّارِبِ وَاللِّحْيَةِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>